{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_06_01_short",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 1話 怜のライバル (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Erika",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-hiraeri001.m4a",
      "text": "……ねぇ、本当にダンサーに戻る気はないの？\nこれからもアイドルとして踊り続けるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey‚ do you really have no intention of returning to being a dancer?\n…Hey‚ do you really have no intention of returning to being a dancer?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。今はアイドルの方が楽しいから\n……それに、一緒に踊りたい仲間がいるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Right now‚ being an idol is more fun for me.\n…Besides‚ I have friends I want to dance with.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数週間前。テレビ番組の収録スタジオ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "--- A few weeks ago‚ at a TV program recording studio",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐ収録が始まるのに、怜はどこに行ったんだ？\n……ん？　あれは……怜が誰かと話しているのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The recording will start soon‚ where did Rei go?\n…Hm? Is that… Rei talking to someone?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "久しぶりね。会うのはいつ以来かしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's been a while. I wonder when was the last time we met.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "台本を見たらあなたの名前があって驚いたわ\n有名アーティストのバックダンサーなんて凄いじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was surprised to see your name in the script.\nBeing a backup dancer for a famous artist is impressive.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "あなたがこんなに頑張ってたなんて\n全然知らなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I had no idea\nyou were doing so well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Erika",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-hiraeri002.m4a",
      "text": "知らなかった？　大人気アイドル様は\n私のことなんて眼中になかったってこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You didn't know? So‚ the popular idol like you\nwasn't even aware of me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Erika",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-hiraeri003.m4a",
      "text": "しばらく会わないうちに、怜は随分偉くなったのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We haven't seen each other for a while‚ but Rei has become a lot better.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "え……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.9,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}